## 3. SRE Metrics for Operational Success

### 3.1 Core SLI/SLO Definitions

| Metric ID | Metric Name | SLI Definition | SLO Target | Error Budget |
|-----------|-------------|----------------|------------|--------------|
| SRE-001 | Pivot Decision Latency | P99 response time for oracle query | ≤ 500ms | 0.1% |
| SRE-002 | Decision Accuracy | Correct predictions / Total predictions | ≥ 85% | 15% |
| SRE-003 | System Availability | Uptime / Total time | ≥ 99.9% | 0.1% |
| SRE-004 | Data Freshness | Age of input data at decision time | ≤ 1 hour | 5% |
| SRE-005 | Rollback Success Rate | Successful rollbacks / Attempted rollbacks | ≥ 99% | 1% |

### 3.2 Pivot-Specific Operational Metrics

```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    PIVOT OPERATIONAL METRICS                           │
├──────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ METRIC               │ FORMULA                                         │
├──────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Pivot Readiness      │ PRS = (1 - TDR) × SS × (1 - CFR) × DF_norm     │
│ Score (PRS)          │ Where: TDR = Tech Debt Ratio                    │
│                      │        SS = System Stability                    │
│                      │        CFR = Change Failure Rate                │
│                      │        DF_norm = Deployment Freq / 10           │
├──────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Operational Risk     │ ORI = (MTTR / 24) × CFR × (1 - SS)             │
│ Index (ORI)          │ Target: ORI < 0.15                              │
├──────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Recovery Capability  │ RCS = (1 - (MTTR / MTTR_max)) × RR × (1 - ORI) │
│ Score (RCS)          │ Where: RR = Reversibility Index                 │
│                      │        MTTR_max = 72 hours                      │
├──────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Pivot Velocity       │ PV = Timeline_days / (BPS × (1 + ORI))         │
│ Index (PVI)          │ Higher = Better execution speed                 │
├──────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Financial Stress     │ FSI = (Pivot_cost + (Burn × Timeline_months))  │
│ Index (FSI)          │       / (Runway_months × Burn)                  │
│                      │ Target: FSI < 0.6                               │
└──────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

